i think i found a solution for you, will try this one


```
const workbookReader = new ExcelJS.stream.xlsx.WorkbookReader(incomingStream, {});
workbookReader.eachSheet((sheet, id) =>
   {
    sheet.eachRow((row, rowIndex) =>
    {
        console.log(row.values);
    }
}
```
